<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Ogilby" baseAuthorityYear="1835" box="[1890,2031,3157,3190]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Epomophorus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="38" pageNumber="96" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gambianus">gambianus</taxonomicName>
species group, and E. reii is a synonym. Taxonomic status of larger subspecies pousarguesi needs further investigation because it is known from just four specimens recorded in two close localities. Former subspecies crypturusis recognized here as a related but distinct species. Two subspecies recognized.
</subSubSection>
